OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1779069821
OL,3,CBurnham seeks to reassure markets but
OL,4,Ckeeps room to bend the rules
OL,6,FThe concern about Andy Burnham is that
OL,7,Fhe could be a bit of a borrower.
OL,9,FIn his interview with ITV News,
OL,10,FBurnham is seeking to reassure markets
OL,11,Fwhile keeping his options open.
OL,13,FAndy Burnham says he supports the idea
OL,14,Fof fiscal rules - self-imposed limits
OL,15,Fon borrowing and spending - as well as
OL,16,F"a plan to get debt down", but he
OL,17,Fstops short of committing to the
OL,18,Fcurrent rules set by Rachel Reeves.
OL,20,F'I support the fiscal rules, there
OL,21,Fneeds to be a plan to get debt down'
OL,26,@xD@AOUxD@YO]
