CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1779069821
OL,3,CBurnham seeks to reassure markets but
OL,4,Ckeeps room to bend the rules
OL,6,FUK bond yields - a measure of the
OL,7,Finterest rates the government pays on
OL,8,Fits debt - are high by historical
OL,9,Fstandards and compared to other
OL,10,Fcountries.
OL,12,FThe UK is perceived as higher risk,
OL,13,Fpartly because of its exposure to the
OL,14,Fsurge in oil and gas prices triggered
OL,15,Fby conflict in the Gulf, but also
OL,16,Fbecause of the political mess in
OL,17,FWestminster.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
