OL,3,CBurnham seeks to reassure markets but
OL,4,Ckeeps room to bend the rules
OL,6,FAs Michael Saunders, a former member
OL,7,Fof the Bank of England's Monetary
OL,8,FPolicy Committee, put it last week: "I
OL,9,Fthink what investors want to see is a
OL,10,Fgovernment that has clear plans to
OL,11,Frein in borrowing, revitalise the
OL,12,Feconomy and improve its popularity -
OL,13,Fso it looks like it will be here for
OL,14,Fthe long run."
